results.name: Travis Scott Medium Olive
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Medium Olive
results.description:
The Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Medium Olive continues the highly coveted collaboration between Jordan Brand and Travis Scott, offering sneakerheads a fresh take on a classic silhouette. Dressed in a striking colorway of medium olive, black, sail, and muslin, this low-top design is instantly recognizable with its iconic reverse swoosh, a signature element of the Travis Scott x Jordan partnership. The premium leather and suede construction provides a tactile contrast, while the standout red Jordan wings logo on the heel and the Cactus Jack branding on the medial side elevate the sneaker’s distinctive style.

Travis Scott’s collaboration with Jordan has had an undeniable influence on sneaker culture, making each new release a must-have for collectors. The reverse swoosh, initially introduced with the first collaboration, has become synonymous with the Travis Scott brand, and this Jordan 1 Low model amplifies that signature aesthetic. Alongside the bold swoosh, other details like the sail midsole, muslin accents, and custom Travis Scott logos give the sneaker a blend of vintage appeal and modern streetwear edge, making it a versatile option for any look.

Released on September 28, 2024, the Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Medium Olive retailed at $150. This medium olive, black, sail, and muslin colorway continues to build on the legacy of the Jordan x Travis Scott collaboration, offering a sneaker that is a key piece of today’s sneaker fashion. Whether you're a dedicated Jordan collector or a fan of streetwear culture, this release is sure to make a statement.

results.name: Travis Scott Canary (Women's)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (Women's)
results.description:
Immerse yourself in the stylish and bold world of the Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (Women's), a sneaker that brings a fresh vibe to a classic silhouette. This edition is splashed in Canary, Racer Blue, and Light Silver hues, embodying the energy of Travis Scott's alma mater, Elkins High School. The sneaker’s design is highlighted by the iconic reversed Swoosh, a hallmark of Travis Scott’s transformative touch to the Jordan 1 & sneaker culture. Adorned with the Cactus Jack logo, these sneakers are a true testament to the rapper's influence and aesthetic.

The Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary is a piece of wearable art. Crafted with premium materials for comfort and durability, the design also features a gum medium brown outsole that complements the vibrant upper, ensuring these shoes stand out in any crowd. The combination of Travis Scott's unique style and Jordan Brand's legendary craftsmanship offers wearers a mix of street-worthy appeal and high-fashion sensibility.

Released on May 17, 2024, the Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (Women's) was retailed for $150. Each pair reflects the spirit of innovation and youth, capturing the essence of Travis Scott's creative vision and the enduring legacy of the Jordan brand. With each step, wearers celebrate a legacy of musical prowess and sneaker history, making it a coveted addition to any collection.

results.name: Travis Scott Medium Olive (PS)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Medium Olive (PS)

results.name: Travis Scott Medium Olive (TD)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Medium Olive (TD)

results.name: Travis Scott Black Phantom
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom
results.description:
Travis Scott closed out 2022 with the return of his signature Jordan 1 Low, this time in a new Black Phantom colorway.

The silhouette returned with his signature backwards Nike Swoosh but with a new contrast stitch design. The all black nubuck sneakers feature a Nike Air logo on the tongue and an Air Jordan Wings logo on the right heel tab. Red, Black, and White/Black laces are included and an embroidered Bee is located on the heel tab of the left sneaker inspired by Travis’ daughter, Stormi.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom released December 15, 2022 with a retail price of $150.

results.name: Travis Scott Olive (Women's)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive (Women's)
results.description:
Travis Scott is back in 2023, following up his previous release of the Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Phantom in 2022, with another Air Jordan 1 Retro Low collaboration. The Jordan 1 Retro low OG SP Travis Scott Olive released exclusively in womens sizing.

The Air Jordan 1 Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive is constructed with white leather and black nubuck uppers. Travis continued to use his signautre reverse style Nike Swoosh, in an olive green colorway. The limited edition sneakers have an aged midsole that sits on top of an olive green outsole.

The women's-exclusive Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive released April 26, 2023, with a retail price of $150.

results.name: Travis Scott Sail
results.title: Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott Sail
results.description:
The Air Jordan Cut The Check TR Travis Scott Sail was born from a collaboration between the Jordan brand and renowned rap artist Travis Scott and features unique design elements and personal touches that reflect his distinct style and creative vision.

This shoe’s upper is crafted from dark brown canvas and off-white leather overlays for a high-contrast aesthetic and lasting durability. It features a traditional lace closure and an adjustable midfoot strap for a secure fit, as well as a foam midsole for shock absorption and energy return. A gum rubber outsole rises from the shoe’s lower edge to its sidewalls and provides a strong grip on many surfaces.

What our experts especially enjoy about the Air Jordan Cut The Check TR Travis Scott Sail, however, is the contrasting red accents on the Jumpman icon and Cactus Jack face logo that can be found on the shoe’s tongue and heel, respectively. This shoe originally retailed for $200 on April 30, 2024.

results.name: Travis Scott Reverse Mocha
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Reverse Mocha
results.description:
Nodding to the Air Jordan 1 High Travis Scott Mocha, the Air Jordan 1 Low Travis Scott Reverse Mocha offers a similar Mocha and off-white palette but in a reverse-style color blocking. Its upper is constructed with a Mocha Durabuck base, white leather overlays, and signature reverse Swooshes. Hits of red on the Wings logo heel embroidery and woven tongue label gives a sharp contrast to the design's neutral look. From there, a yellowed Air sole adds a vintage feel.

The Air Jordan 1 Low Travis Scott Reverse Mocha released in July of 2022 and retailed for $190.

results.name: Travis Scott British Khaki
results.title: Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott British Khaki
results.description:
Travis Scott and Jordan Brand teamed up to deliver the Air Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott British Khaki. The British Khaki marks the second time that Travis has added his touch to the Jordan 6 silhouette, the first being the 2019 Air Jordan 6 Travis Scott.

The upper of the Air Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott British Khaki is made of British Khaki suede. From there, hits of Bright Crimson appear on the heel and tongue embroidered logos. The upper also has two cargo pockets: one with a snap enclosure on the lateral ankle and one with a zip enclosure on the medial ankle. A translucent tongue, heel tab, and outsole that glows in the dark adds the finishing touches to this latest Travis Scott Jordan.

The Air Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott British Khaki released in April of 2021 and retailed for $250.

results.name: Fragment x Travis Scott
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Fragment x Travis Scott
results.description:
The Air Jordan 1 Low Fragment Design x Travis Scott nods to the original 2016 Air Jordan 1 Fragment with its simple color blocking. It features a smooth white leather upper with black and royal blue leather overlays. From there, a signature reversed Swoosh and yellowed soles add a Cactus Jack flair to the classic silhouette.

The Air Jordan 1 Low Fragment Design x Travis Scott released in August of 2021 and retailed for $150.

results.name: Travis Scott Cactus Jack Saturn Gold
results.title: Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Saturn Gold
results.description:
In collaboration with Travis Scott's record label Cactus Jack, the Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Saturn Gold pays homage to outdoor exploration and the Nike ACG Pocket Knife hiking shoe. It boasts a light yellow layered mesh upper with matching Durabuck overlays and reversed Swoosh logos. A drawstring Gillie lacing system nods to common features on trail runners. At the base, a yellowed sole with a cloudy Air unit adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Saturn Gold released in May of 2022 and retailed for $150.

results.name: Travis Scott Mocha
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro High OG SP Travis Scott Mocha
results.description:
The first release as part of Travis Scott's monumental partnership with Nike, the Air Jordan 1 Travis Scott breaks the conventional rules of the Air Jordan 1 design. For starters, the side Swooshes are reversed, which each tailing facing the toe. Woven tongue tags are shifted and stitched to the side of the tongue instead of the top. Also, in the collar, there is a hidden stash pocket. A one-of-a-kind design fit for a one-of-a-kind artist.

The Air Jordan 1 Travis Scott features a white leather upper with Mocha suede overlays and black leather reversed Swooshes. Hits of red on the tongue slightly contrast the design's earth tones. On the heel, a debossed Cactus Jack logo adds a custom feel. From there, a yellowed midsole and matching Mocha outsole complete the design.

The Jordan 1 Travis Scott Mocha released in May 2019 and retailed for $175.

To shop all Air Jordan 1 shoes, click here.

results.name: White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition)
results.title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition)
results.description:
Unveiled on July 28, 2023, the Nike Air Force 1 Low Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition is more than just a sneaker; it's the embodiment of Travis’ creative genius, this shoe echoes with the sounds and themes of his groundbreaking album, 'Utopia’.

Radiating in a dominant all-white shade, this iconic silhouette carries the legacy of the Air Force 1 with a touch of Travis Scott's unique artistry. Crafted with precision, the sneaker showcases the word 'Utopia' imprinted on its heel - a direct nod to Scott's most recent album.

But there's more. The Utopia graphic doesn't just serve aesthetic vibes; it’s a celebration of music and streetwear colliding. The fusion of leather and subtle design details crafts an aesthetic that's both sleek and statement-making. Dive into the Utopia with this pair of sneakers that retailed at $150.

Please note: by listing this item for sale, you agree to ship within the normal shipping window. Shipping deadlines will not be extended to accommodate shipping delays from the retailer.

results.name: Travis Scott Cactus Jack Baroque Brown
results.title: Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Baroque Brown
results.description:
In collaboration with Travis Scott's record label Cactus Jack, the Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Brown draws inspiration from the Nike ACG Pocket Knife hiking shoe. It features a layered mesh upper with tonal-brown Durabuck overlays and reversed Swoosh logos. A drawstring Gillie lacing system nods to common features on trail runners. At the base, a yellowed sole with a cloudy Air unit completes the design.

The Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Brown released in May of 2022 and retailed for $150.

results.name: Travis Scott Wheat
results.title: Nike Air Trainer 1 SP Travis Scott Wheat
results.description:
Drawing inspiration from hiking culture and gear, the Nike Air Trainer 1 SP Travis Scott Grey Wheat arrives in a dark brown canvas construction with matching mesh overlays and single stitch Swoosh logos. Canvas shrouds on the upper give wearers options for styling. At the heel and inside of the tongue, concealed zipper pockets provide extra storage. From there, "Cactus Corporation" insignias at the heel and forefoot velcro strap complete the design.

The Nike Air Trainer 1 SP Travis Scott Wheat released in May of 2022 and retailed for $160.

results.name: Travis Scott Canary (PS)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (PS)
results.description:
The Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (PS) is a "Special Project (SP)" sneaker, which means it’s created in the Nike lab and incorporates premium materials. This sneaker is also a collaborative project between American rapper Travis Scott and the Jordan Brand.

The white leather construction serves as a backdrop for Canary, Racer Blue, and red accents, which intentionally use the kid-friendly primary colors. The forefoot overlays, the toebox mudguard, the heel panel, the laces, the heel tab, the tongue, and the collar lining come in bright Canary, which contrasts with the Racer Blue Swoosh logo on the side panels. In terms of branding, the heel tab displays the Jordan Wings logo, the red "NIKE" lettering graces the tongue tab, and the "cactus jack" in red is printed on the inner side panel.

Our StockX experts like the inclusion of one reverse Swoosh and one standard Swoosh. The preschool-sized Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (PS) was launched on May 25, 2024, and sold for $65.

results.name: Travis Scott Grey Haze
results.title: Nike Air Trainer 1 SP Travis Scott Grey Haze
results.description:
Pulling inspiration from backpacking gear, the Nike Air Trainer 1 SP Travis Scott Grey Haze features a light grey canvas upper with darker grey mesh overlays and single stitch Swoosh logos. Canvas shrouds on the upper give wearers options for styling. At the heel and inside of the tongue, concealed zipper pockets provide extra storage. From there, "Cactus Corporation" insignias at the heel and forefoot velcro strap add a custom feel.

The Nike Air Trainer 1 SP Travis Scott Grey released in May of 2022 and retailed for $160.

results.name: Travis Scott
results.title: Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott
results.description:
Trailing the buzz of their recent collaborations, Travis Scott and Jordan Brand team up once again for the Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott, now available on StockX. This is the fourth Air Jordan silhouette that Cactus Jack has touched. This sneaker made its mainstream debut when Travis rocked them on stage during his Super Bowl LIII performance and the rest is history.

This AJ 6 features an olive upper with black detailing and red contrasting accents on the tongue and lace locks. A side cargo pocket is displayed on the collar, giving this sneaker a design modification that makes it the first of its kind. A sail midsole, glow-in-the-dark translucent outsole, 3M detailing and both Nike Air and Cactus Jack branding on the heel completes the design. These sneakers released in October of 2019 for $250.

results.name: Travis Scott Cactus Jack
results.title: Nike Mac Attack QS SP Travis Scott Cactus Jack
results.description:
The Nike Mac Attack QS SP Travis Scott Cactus Jack is unveiled in an engaging Light Smoke Grey, Black, and White color combination, incorporating a mix of leather and mesh across its upper. The mesh is prominently featured on the vamp and side panels, while high-quality leather forms the majority of the shoe’s construction.

This sneaker stands out with its gray and black color scheme, infused with the signature Travis Scott flair. The sneaker's standout feature is the iconic reverse Swoosh in black leather, adding a rebellious edge to its appearance. The Cactus Jack logo, embroidered on the spine, and a blue and black checkerboard pattern on the tongue tag add unique Travis Scott touches, completing the overall look.

What sets this sneaker apart is its functional design and comfortable fit. It features a white rubber midsole and a grey outsole, ensuring durability and stability. The Travis Scott x Nike Mac Attack QS SP Cactus Jack is set to release on December 19, 2023, at a retail price of $120, offering a perfect blend of style and performance for sneaker enthusiasts.

results.name: Travis Scott University Red
results.title: Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott University Red
results.description:
The release of the Air Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott University Red marks a momentous occasion: the first wide public launch of a brand-new, original colorway from the collaborative genius of Jordan Brand and Travis Scott. This sneaker is a homage to the past and a forward leap in design, drawing inspiration from classic basketball sneakers of the '80s and the rugged aesthetic of '90s skate shoes. It’s a perfect blend for enthusiasts who appreciate a retro vibe with a modern twist.

Travis Scott's first entirely original silhouette comes to life with the iconic, signature reversed Nike Swoosh in a bold university red, contrasting strikingly against the timeless sail & black upper. The carefully pre-yellowed midsole adds a touch of vintage appeal, invoking a sense of nostalgia while remaining at the pinnacle of style. Complete with a special co-branded shoe box and dust bag, the Jordan Jumpman Jack TR is as much a collector's piece as it is a testament to sneaker innovation.

Released on April 26, 2024, the Air Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott University Red retailed for $200. This sneaker is the inception of Travis Scott's original design legacy, offering a unique take on sneaker culture. With its rich 80s and 90s influences and the unmatched Travis Scott brand power, this sneaker is ready to conquer the streets and capture the essence of both basketball and skateboarding heritage.

results.name: Travis Scott Neutral Olive
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Travis Scott Neutral Olive
results.description:
Indulge in the golf course's lush greens with the Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Travis Scott Neutral Olive, a stellar collaboration between the iconic Jordan brand and the renowned rapper, Travis Scott. This is the first-ever golf shoe collaboration between Jordan and Travis Scott, making it a rare treasure in the sneaker community.

Reflecting Cactus Jack’s signature earth-toned color palette, this sneaker captivates the crowd with its olive green shade harmoniously blended with sail-tinted leather overlays, a contrasting black reverse Swoosh logo, and subtle touches of bright volt green on the tongue label and heel logo. Crafted for golf enthusiasts, yet with a design that resonates with every sneakerhead, this pair is tailored for the greens with altered traction and hardened rubber. However, the cool and casual vibe it carries makes it suitable for off-the-green casual struts, giving Travis Scott fans a chance to sport these beauties anytime, anywhere.

Dropped on October 13, 2023, at a retail price of $170, the Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Travis Scott Neutral Olive is not just a pair of sneakers; it's a statement of style, comfort, and unrivaled collaboration between sportswear and music royalty.

results.name: Travis Scott Cactus Jack Wheat Lemon Drop
results.title: Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Wheat Lemon Drop
results.description:
Joining the Gold and Brown version of Nike SNKRS is the Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Wheat Lemon Drop sneaker in baroque brown, wheat, and lemon drop colorways.

The Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Wheat Lemon Drop silhouette is constructed with a lemon-colored upper mesh and a baroque brown mudguard and heel tab. To complete the design is a baroque brown corporate branding, red rope laces, wheat-colored tongues, and overlays, including a reverse Swoosh on the lateral in a neural lemon drop hue.

The Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Wheat Lemon Drop sneaker was released on May 2022, retailing at $160.

results.name: Travis Scott Canary (TD)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (TD)
results.description:
The Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (TD) is a Special Project (SP) sneaker launched by American rapper Travis Scott and Jordan Brand. This means it’s crafted in the Nike lab using premium materials and design patterns.

This low-top sneaker boasts an all-leather upper construction with a light silver base and overlays in bright Canary. Although the reinforced stitching is tonal, it appears oversized due to the sneaker’s small size. Large Swoosh logos in Racer Blue check across the side panels, while a woven tongue tag bears "NIKE" lettering in crimson. The upper sits on a durable rubber outsole, which features a standard traction pattern and a Gum Medium Brown hue.

Our StockX experts like Travis Scott’s CACTUS JACK branding, which can be found beneath the Swoosh, on the inner side panel, in crimson ink. The toddler-sized Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Canary (TD) was launched on May 25, 2024, and sold for $50.

results.name: Travis Scott
results.title: Nike SB Dunk Low Travis Scott
results.description:
Travis Scott teamed up with Nike SB to release his first official skate shoe, the Nike SB Dunk Low Travis Scott, now available on StockX. This design follows a similar design aesthetic as seen on the Air Force 1 Low Travis Scott Cactus Jack, featuring an array of materials and prints. Unlike previous Travis Scott releases, these were not available on SNKRS and only available at select Nike SB stockists.

This Nike SB Dunk Low is composed of suede upper with paisley canvas and plaid flannel overlays. As the paisley overlays wear off, an elephant print is revealed. Embroidered text around the collar, rope laces, and La Flame’s Cactus Jack logo on the puffy tongues completes this design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $150.

results.name: Travis Scott Mocha
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Mocha
results.description:
Building off the success of their previous collaborations, Travis Scott adds yet another new design to his collaborative relationship with Jumpman via the Air Jordan 1 Low Travis Scott, now available on StockX. Travis teased the release of this shoe while on his Astroworld tour, leaving fans of both his music and the Jordan Brand alike with one question: When are these shoes dropping? On the Friday night of July 19, 2019, Travis answered the masses by making them available on his website, with a release on the SNKRS app following the next day.

This AJ 1 Low features a black upper with dark brown overlays and red accents on the branding. Much like the Air Jordan 1 High Travis Scott, La Flame added his signature backwards Swoosh logo on the lateral side. "Cactus Jack" insignias on the heel and inner upper atopa sail midsole and dark brown outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in July of 2019 and retailed for $130.

results.name: Travis Scott Cactus Jack
results.title: Jordan 4 Retro Travis Scott Cactus Jack
results.description: The only way to describe the Travis Scott Air Jordan 4 Retros properly would be to use the rappers own adlib: la flame. These Jordan 4s were made in collaboration with rapper, Travis Scott and nicknamed the "Cactus Jack" edition. Similar in design to the infamous Eminem pair, these feature a lighter shade of blue suede on the upper. Black accents, a red liner, paint splatter detailing, a white midsole and "Cactus Jack" branding on the back heel tab finish things off for this pair. These dropped in June of 2018 for $225 and came exclusively in men’s sizes. If you’re a fan of Travis Scott and the AJ 4, this pair is another must-have. Straight up!

results.name: Travis Scott Cactus Trails
results.title: Nike Air Max 270 React ENG Travis Scott Cactus Trails
results.description:
Nike and Travis Scott teamed up once again to deliver the Nike Air Max 270 React Travis Scott, now available on StockX. This is the first time La Flame has put his signature touch on an Air Max silhouette.

This Air Max 270 consists of a mesh upper with tumblr leather and suede overlays. A gold midsole, green tongue with attached lace locks, and Cactus Jack branding on the heel tabs completes the design. These sneakers released in May of 2020 and retailed for $170.

results.name: Travis Scott Cactus Jack
results.title: Nike Air Force 1 Low Travis Scott Cactus Jack
results.description:
Travis Scott and Nike add a new design to their growing Air Force arsenal with the Air Force 1 Low Travis Scott Cactus Jack, now available on StockX. After a year of sneaker world dominance, Nike is adding a twist to their latest collaborative AF 1 with Cactus Jack. This new design features a never before seen detachable lace cover that encloses with a heavy brass zipper.

This Travis AF-1 features a patchwork upper comprised of camouflage, corduroy, duck canvas, flannel, leather, suede and wool. Unmistakable Cactus Jack insignias are placed throughout the silhouette. A sail midsole and gum rubber outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in November of 2019 and retailed for $160.

results.name: Fragment x Travis Scott
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro High OG SP Fragment x Travis Scott
results.description:
The Air Jordan 1 High OG SP Fragment Design x Travis Scott fragment draws inspiration from a Jordan 1 Royal press sample from 1985 with its white and blue tumbled leather upper. Similar to previous Travis Scott Jordan 1s, signature reverse Swooshes and hidden stash pockets in the collar add on to the classic design. From there, both Travis Scott's Cactus Jack and Fragment logos are debossed in black on the heel wrap.

The Air Jordan 1 High OG SP Fragment Design x Travis Scott released in July of 2021 and retailed for $200.

results.name: Travis Scott Olive (PS)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive (PS)
results.description:
The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive PS is a collaborative sneaker by Travis Scott and the Jordan Brand in pre-school sizing.

This Air Jordan 1 features an upper made of a Black suede base with Sail leather overlays on the forefoot, eyestays, and heel. Medium Olive on the suede Swooshes and University Red accents on the tongue, heel, and insole branding contrast the upper. Other details include reverse lateral Swooshes, Cactus Jack branding on the nylon tongue, White laces, and mismatched branding on the heel and insole featuring Cactus Jack and Jordan logos. A Sail midsole and a Medium Olive Green rubber outsole complete the design. Each pair comes with an extra set of laces.

What our experts love about this Air Jordan 1 sneaker is the design and colorway. The Olive Green colorway with Black/University Red/ White accents and collaborative branding details throughout make this sneaker stand out. The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive PS was released on April 26th, 2023, for a retail price of $60.

results.name: Travis Scott Black Phantom (PS)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom (PS)
results.description:
The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom PS is a collaborative sneaker for pre-schoolers.

This model features an all-black upper with Phantom stitching throughout. Collaborative details include Travis Scott’s reverse Swoosh on the lateral with the normal Swoosh on the medial, Cactus Jack branding on the tongue and insoles, and the rapper’s name inversely written on the right sock liner. A black sole unit and mismatched branding on the back heel with the Wings logo on the right shoe and a bee logo on the left one complete the design.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom PS was released on December 15th, 2022, retailing at $60.

results.name: Travis Scott Black Phantom (TD)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom (TD)
results.description:
The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom TD, designed for toddlers, is a collaborative sneaker between Nike and the American musician.

This Low Air Jordan 1 features a nubuck and suede upper in a black/phantom tone with contrast white stitching. The rapper’s trademark reverse Swoosh is visible on the lateral, with the normal facing Swoosh on the medial. A woven Nike tag on the tongue, Cactus Jack branding on the sock liner, mismatched heel tabs displaying the Wings logo, and a bee graphic, plus a black rubber cupsole complete the design.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom TD was released on December 15th, 2022, retailing at $50.

results.name: Travis Scott Olive (TD)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive (TD)
results.description:
The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive TD is a limited edition shoe that was made in toddler sizing and takes inspiration from both the Air Jordan 1 and the creative talents of Travis Scott.

The Travis Scott Olive TD Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP has a Sail and Black colorway with pops of University Red and Medium Olive. The upper is made from suede and leather upper with a Medium Olive Nike Swoosh on the side. The outsole is made of rubber which provides traction and helps to prevent slips and falls. Additionally, the shoe has a cushioned insole that offers comfort and support for extended wear. The tongue features a University Red Swoosh and Nike name while the heel tab has the Air Jordan Wings logo.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Olive TD was released on April 26th, 2023 at a retail price of $50.

results.name: Travis Scott Sail (TD)
results.title: Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott Sail (TD)
results.description:
The Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott Sail (TD) is part of the Travis Scott x Jordan collaboration, which released the rapper’s first signature shoe with the renowned footwear label.

Like the adult-sized version, this toddler-sized shoe features a high-contrast upper with a canvas-like base in Dark Mocha and leather overlays in Sail. These overlays cross the heel and form a strap across the forefoot. In addition to the Velcro strap, a front lace closure with cotton laces in Sail secures the shoe. The outer side displays a reverse Swoosh in Muslin, while the other side features a standard Swoosh. Other branding details include Travis Scott’s signature smiley face on the heel and a red Jumpman logo on the tongue.

Our experts at StockX like the choice of tan rubber on the outsole because it looks like traditional gum. The toddler-sized Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott Sail (TD) was released on April 30, 2024, and sold for $75.

results.name: Travis Scott Sail (PS)
results.title: Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott Sail (PS)
results.description:
The Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott Sail (PS) adds an earthy, neutral colorway to American rapper Travis Scott’s first signature sneaker with the Air Jordan brand.

What makes this sneaker stand out is the use of a canvas-like material on the upper. This durable yet breathable material comes in Dark Mocha and has a rougher texture than traditional leather. The sneaker features a lace closure and a leather forefoot overlay in Sail that forms a strap across the toe area. This strap displays Travis Scott branding and attaches with Velcro. A reverse Swoosh in Muslin stretches across the outer side panel, while the other panel displays a normal Swoosh logo. Crimson details can be found on the tongue’s Jumpman logo and the signature Travis Scott smiley face on the heel.

Our StockX experts like the rubber outsole, which features a traditional gum tone. The preschool-sized Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott Sail (PS) was released on April 30, 2024, and retailed at $90.

results.name: Travis Scott Reverse Mocha (PS)
results.title: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Reverse Mocha (PS)
results.description:
The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Reverse Mocha (Preschool) was initially available for sale in July of 2022. This shoe model’s first starting retail price was $150.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Reverse Mocha (Preschool) has a mocha-colored base with a variety of white and cream overlays. On the heel of the shoe, there is red detailing. The sole of the sneaker is also in a mocha color and provides standard traction.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Reverse Mocha (Preschool) Swoosh is reversed and appears in a cream color with matching laces.

results.name: White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's)
results.title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's)
results.description:
Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's) is a collaboration between Nike and Los Angeles-based hip-hop artist Travis Scott. It celebrates the release of Scott’s album "Utopia" and paints the Air Force 1 Low in an all-white colorway.

The women’s size sneaker boasts an upper created entirely from leather with tonal overlays and an understated Swoosh. Providing breathability and detailing, perforations can be found across the vamp and along the side panels. The word "utopia" and Cactus Jack branding in curving gold letters are screened onto the heel. These are the only elements identifying this sneaker as a Travis Scott collaboration.

Our experts like the Nike Air midsole, which also comes in a clean white. The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's) was released on July 29th, 2023, and retailed at $150.

results.name: Travis Scott (GS)
results.title: Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott (GS)
results.description:
The Air Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott GS is a product of the collaboration between Houston-born artist Travis Scott and sportswear brand Nike.

A variation of the Air Jordan 6 Retro, this shoe features an Olive nubuck upper with an Infrared logo inscribed on its heel, a frayed tongue, perforations on its sides, and reflective detailing. Like the Air Jordan 1 Travis Scott rendition, this sneaker for grade-schoolers features a stash pocket on its ankle. The upper rests on an Air midsole which lies on a black rubber outsole with patterns for traction.

The Air Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott GS was released on 11th October 2019. At the time, its retail price was $160.

results.name: Travis Scott Sail
results.title: Nike Air Force 1 Low Travis Scott Sail
results.description: With Astroworld upon us, its about time Cactus Jack blessed us with a new pair of kicks too. This time, Nike boy Travis Scott linked up with the Swoosh on another colorway of the Air Force 1 Low silhouette. With nearly identical features as its predecessor, this model features a sail canvas upper with reinforced stitching. Naturally though, the most eye catching features on this pair are the chromed out Nike Swoosh on both the lateral and medial sides and the Cactus Jack patch on top of the laces. This pair is finished off with a clean gum bottom. The Air Force 1 Low Travis Scott Sail released in exclusive numbers in August 2018 for $150.

results.name: Travis Scott (Special Box)
results.title: Nike SB Dunk Low Travis Scott (Special Box)
results.description:
Travis Scott teamed up with Nike SB to release his first official skate shoe, the Nike SB Dunk Low Travis Scott (Regular Box), now available on StockX. This design follows a similar design aesthetic as seen on the Air Force 1 Low Travis Scott Cactus Jack, featuring an array of materials and prints. This special box release was exclusive to Travis Scott’s website via online raffle.

This Nike SB Dunk Low is composed of suede upper with paisley canvas and plaid flannel overlays. As the paisley overlays wear off, an elephant print is revealed. Embroidered text around the collar, rope laces, and La Flame’s Cactus Jack logo on the puffy tongues completes this design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $150.
